### Create Task
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

{
  "title": "Implement task API",
  "description": "Create handlers and routing",
  "priority": 2,
  "tags": ["backend", "fiber"]
}

